  "title": "Mildly Sour Syrian Courgettes Stew",
  "description": "A traditional Syrian dish featuring courgettes, double-rise-bread, and ayurvedic-tamasic-friendly ingredients to help cure hangovers, this stew is sour, chewy, and full of flavor. It is a popular comfort food in Syria.",
