  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced courgettes and cook until they are tender.",
    "Add the sumac, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the torn bread and stir to combine.",
    "Add the lemon juice and water, and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer the stew for 20 minutes.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with additional sumac if desired."
